---
title: Spinach and Tofu Dahl with coriander and lime
description: Golden crispy tofu is coated in lime juice and coriander and dunked into delicious spinach dahl in this simple yet surprising protein-packed veggie recipe.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R07_W10_IE_IEXVV17785-2_Main_R_high-70b93cf6.jpg
